d":1810882,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a3354946537b9db7cbf05d401c6341f07ee9042","tid":1810882,"uid":77092,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:02:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:08:42.000Z","msg":"真係好鐘意呢兩句 完全將兩個年紀嘅兩種心態表達到出黎<br />\n有時可能用兩三年時間已經由第一種心態過渡到第二種心態 睇番感覺好神奇"},{"pid":"5cca1d103aa03d5b94d26ad756e3a94308281abd","tid":1810882,"uid":169116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"當你覺得做人幼稚其實比較好嘅時候就代表你已經成熟了。"},{"pid":"fad7b70ea367a851cf3550582d7b47813de345a7","tid":1810882,"uid":49944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"受打擊"},{"pid":"6856687b5672a9f1c77fee60819178af73d80828","tid":1810882,"uid":24098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"識理解其他人感受"},{"pid":"6e3827021c4ee1223846b89eb463697426506680","tid":1810882,"uid":22692,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f82844840fdc9778dd5598017345afc065cb3b45","tid":1810882,"uid":226387,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fed9034705ade34497118dbf988d7eae6b12655b","tid":1810882,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd1f19a8efb966e98e13009266fb288932c671bb","tid":1810882,"uid":262093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:41:12.000Z","msg":"睇多啲書"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:45:26.000Z","msg":"咩類型?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:08:02.000Z","msg":"哲學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:46:22.000Z","msg":"哲學唔會令人成熟 唔好傻"},{"pid":"e8043a5b9f316c018389b64f887d6c1465683dc2","tid":1810882,"uid":28068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"你又唔講幾成熟<br />\n點幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27483dbebcdd33a0382f7d930ff7975738c0e891","tid":1810882,"uid":28068,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"當你發現自己懷念以前3成熟既自己<br />\n你就10成熟了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd436264bf8451bea37af9e0f089f635a3c162b","tid":1810882,"uid":343059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:20:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"faf8b589d779e181cf9c744a41448821c2c9baf9","tid":1810882,"uid":265225,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T18:16:54.000Z","msg":"出去識多啲人，了解吓其他同自己唔同嘅人&mdash; 你做唔做到愛所有人呢？就算係自己嘅敵人？當你學識多啲設身處地，你就會明白多咗好多點解其他人會咁，而呢樣嘢可以幫你建立同理心<br />\n<br />\n學識好多野唔係非黑即白，呢樣嘢都需要經歷，所以多啲識唔同嘅人都會有幫助。原來有好多野唔係話一定啱一定錯，原來世界上有好多種生活嘅可能性，唔係只係得你認知嘅幾種。原來好多連登感情台上面講嘅嘢都係好膚淺嘅道德審判。當你唔再道德批判身邊嘅人，明白每個人做每樣嘢有自己嘅原因，當你真正領悟到呢樣嘢，就會多咗一分對人嘅包容<br />\n<br />\n了解多啲自己&mdash; 其實你係一個咩人？如果要形容你嘅核心價值，你會點形容？你最重視嘅係知識？係人同人之間嘅關係？自由？安全感？你心底最害怕嘅係咩？你最想得到嘅人生係點樣？有啲咩阻住你追求你想要嘅人生？<br />\n<br />\n當你知道自己最想要嘅係咩之後，多啲發展自己想要嘅人生，令自己快樂。當你可以令到自己快樂，當你唔再咁介意身邊人嘅諗法，因為你好清楚自己做緊咩，你好comfortable with who you are，你好清楚自己喺世界上嘅價值，唔需要特登證明俾任何人睇，就算有人誤解你，你都能夠處之泰然並且包容及寬恕。無需向世界高呼你嘅成就，亦無需刻意貶低自己，你就又成熟一點了。"},{"pid":"77f56696cc8b07f26a6babe93e7e5b5115375cb4","tid":1810882,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5841769b30e1a19e5da8ca67da14247f41b2753c","tid":1810882,"uid":170176,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:47:34.000Z","msg":"同多啲唔同嘅人相處<br />\n自自然然侍人處事都會成熟啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T21:45:58.000Z","msg":"近呢1,2年已經多咗同唔同人相處，但係我都係冇變過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個細路咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時細過我嘅人會以為我仲細過佢，會照顧返我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6736576c554fc9fc2704ad091e552239c6c65f4","tid":1810882,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3177927e2894885fa8df9c61a6734d9a72a6484d","tid":1810882,"uid":12909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df5115386ee0735bd07a1b226d3cbcbd4fbe8cea","tid":1810882,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:40:52.000Z","msg":"你其實講得好啱 但我唔知點改"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"做咩咁講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對方話你唔夠成熟？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T21:50:56.000Z","msg":"幾年前講lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到最近又聽到身邊新識嘅人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />先知自己幾年黎都冇改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲以為人大咗就自然會變得成熟"},{"pid":"48917520bc0a5aa2f8efe4a89b67f95fbc1690ff","tid":1810882,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2b16cafb00fa973172329d06a254ba4be3df1af","tid":1810882,"uid":209107,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:03:02.000Z","msg":"要有一次深刻嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T21:55:29.000Z","msg":"有 <span style=\"font-size: small;\">仲爭d自殺</span> 但係睇開咗之後我仲係keep住保持真我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01d7b1ba6562ae3d7df132dc048f25a9421a8d9","tid":1810882,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c14d4caeacb29183f49209df2be2c09d20d2d4aa","tid":1810882,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:03:32.000Z","msg":"有自己主見<br />\n不會受人影響"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T21:56:03.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ff4dcda67ec250e71e02846eaa3d2cae3b81f8","tid":1810882,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79aa92907785c9c3817695fd3ee83f382d6427dc","tid":1810882,"uid":312130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"唔好咁on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T21:56:38.000Z","msg":"好。。。<